    "name": "PIT OF GOBLIN",
    "steam_appid": 3253530,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是否曾想象过成为最低等的存在，过着连老鼠都瞧不起的肮脏生活？在《地精之渊》中，这就是你的日常！穿上你那臭气熏天的靴子，在快要崩塌的坟墓、阴森恐怖的洞穴和鬼魂肆虐的废墟中徘徊，每一步都充满危险与惊悚！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要满足地精王的无底胃口。万幸的是，你可以拖着你的地精小伙伴们陪你一起受苦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>携手合作或制造混乱</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/d3dc146fe0b484ddf735aef74c166d34.poster.avif?t=1771518176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/d3dc146fe0b484ddf735aef74c166d34.webm?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/d3dc146fe0b484ddf735aef74c166d34.mp4?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可与最多3名其他地精小伙伴组队。团队合作至关重要……当然，除非你是那种喜欢捣乱的地精！你们是会团结一致，还是会偷偷搞恶作剧？无论如何，这都将是地精式的混乱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/ebb96d62d37b6cb54322fc901026a83e.poster.avif?t=1771518176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/ebb96d62d37b6cb54322fc901026a83e.webm?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/ebb96d62d37b6cb54322fc901026a83e.mp4?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一次在地渊中的蹒跚前行，都是独一无二的地精传奇，不论你是在机敏地规避着致命的陷阱，还是无奈地被自己那双硕大的脚丫绊倒。每一次探险，都是一场不可复制的经历。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着探索的不断深入，面临的挑战就越发艰巨。切记，若是你想活到明天，就得找到出路……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你是出于贪婪，还是精于策略？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/1eb8e3111c89974747da41298f9372fd.poster.avif?t=1771518176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/1eb8e3111c89974747da41298f9372fd.webm?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/1eb8e3111c89974747da41298f9372fd.mp4?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在搜寻食物的过程中，你需要抉择：是将辛苦得来的战利品上交给地精王，还是自行享用以增强体力，又或是拿到商店出售以备将来探险之需——但稍有差池，就可能让你的地精生涯就此终结。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可别忘了，地精王的胃口深似海，无论多少食物……甚至地精，他都能照单全收！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>诡异的笑声和地精的意外</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/f3a251ea496eeafb00ee9aa8f8a7b8ee.poster.avif?t=1771518176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/f3a251ea496eeafb00ee9aa8f8a7b8ee.webm?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/f3a251ea496eeafb00ee9aa8f8a7b8ee.mp4?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在那座阴森诡异的地牢中蹒跚前行，就连你的脚趾甲都会不由自主地蜷缩起来！不论是面对那些令人毛骨悚然的坟墓、被诅咒的走廊，还是目睹地精们那些笨拙滑稽的动作，这座地渊之下，无一不充满挑战……也不会安宁。在这里，每一顿饭的获取都仿佛是在进行一场惊心动魄的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战利品、贪婪与地精的荣耀！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/73f684515a842cd3f2fe8240608ba9c3.poster.avif?t=1771518176\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/73f684515a842cd3f2fe8240608ba9c3.webm?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253530/extras/73f684515a842cd3f2fe8240608ba9c3.mp4?t=1771518176\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是会选择囤积战利品以确保自己的生存，还是会秉持保守之策，以博取地精王的欢心？决定权掌握在你自己的手中。每一次深入幽暗的地渊，都是升级装备的绝佳机遇，但切记要谨慎行事，因为一旦令地精王感到失望，那将是你走向毁灭的开始！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏特色</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-4人在线合作游戏</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >语音聊天</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >地牢、城堡、墓穴等各种恐怖场景</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >被可怕的怪物追捕！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >时刻饥饿的国王！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >食物和战利品！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以点燃的木火把！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >火焰……以及友军误伤</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 俄语, 简体中文, 瑞典语, 乌克兰语, 日语",
